  <h1 style="color:#fff;margin:0.5rem 0 0.25rem">About — Ember CSPT Decoding Pipeline</h1>

  <div style="background:#1a1a1a;border:1px solid #333;border-radius:6px;padding:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem">
    <div style="color:#f90;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:8px">Versions Tested</div>
