  <div style="background:#001a00;border:1px solid #4a4;border-radius:6px;padding:1rem">
    <div style="color:#4a4;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:8px">Safe Patterns</div>
    <p style="color:#ccc;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0">
      1. Use <code>window.location.pathname</code> instead of route-recognizer params<br/>
      2. Use <code>*wildcard</code> routes with %2f (star skips final decode)<br/>
      3. Always <code>encodeURIComponent()</code> before interpolating into fetch URLs<br/>
      4. Use double curlies <code>&lbrace;&lbrace;content&rbrace;&rbrace;</code> (HTML-escaped) instead of triple<br/>
      5. Validate params with regex before use: <code>/^[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+$/.test(param)</code>
    </p>
